Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:54.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}張りつめた空気が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:01:00.85,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}高まる鼓動広がってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:07.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深く息吸い込んだなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:12.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう前しか見えないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:17.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰も代わる事出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:20.19,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私しか歩けない道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:23.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その涙も全て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:26.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}輝きはじめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.57,0:01:31.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから思いきり振り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:34.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}手のひらに宿る{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:36.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}迷わずにまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:39.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明日へと行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:43.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ほんのまばたきの瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:46.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えるよ夢の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:48.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}儚くて遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:51.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}諦めないわいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:53.53,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私だけの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:58.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:54.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}喜欢着紧张的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:01:00.85,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}兴奋起来走向更广阔的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:07.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深呼一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:12.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只专注于眼前的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:17.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}谁都无法替代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:20.19,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有我才能前进的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:23.23,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}连同那份泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:26.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全部开始闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.57,0:01:31.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因此将宿于手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:34.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}尽情挥扬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:36.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果断地  径直地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:39.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向着明天全力进发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:43.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在转瞬即逝之间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:46.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}实现那梦中的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:48.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}无论它多么虚幻和遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:51.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也绝不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:53.53,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和仅属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:58.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}竹剑节奏响彻永远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.81,0:00:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:11.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第23话\N谎言与沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃  现在只有你一个？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大家好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是大家在等聪莉啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级的真要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年级就剩下咱俩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  冷清可算是咱们的传统了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然我这个部长再严厉一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  大家都因为前次大赛而情绪低落？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为输掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看咱们部原本不就是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说小珠输掉比赛是让我吃了一惊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但昨天也没什么特别的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该担心的是那个对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋啦…你们来啦…继续吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！快换衣服和我们练习啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等人到齐再说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  彻彻底底地泄气了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！不就是输了场比赛  你这算什么嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这算什么呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就是要被开除嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后比赛还多的是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我们把老师的工作找回来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！纪梨乃！真可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说前次大赛是受了不少打击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们部现在已经上轨道了！机会有的是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的对手不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没那个铃木凛的话就没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇…瞧这马后炮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之  不动手什么也不会开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在教室里找不到自己的眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家一起帮忙找了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠和小都都呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠要值日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都说要去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那个饰品店吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在继续啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  只是店长突然有病所以过去代班
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要开始了！快去换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不好意思我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我要热身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  我很容易被人打脸吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…对方的确打起来很方便…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老师  石田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长先生找您  请立即到校长室来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为比赛输了所以要开除吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你够了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次  小珠交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后的时间…有这么漫长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山和…岩佐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像是和外校的学生打架斗殴后逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有学生受轻伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想让他们暂时休学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是剑道部的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.19,0:08:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生这种事情还真是棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人说运动部也有连带责任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个  特别是外山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这个人特别暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有人提出要剑道部休部一年…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！其他的人又没有责任！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还没有决定呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太不讲理了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个做的事情和剑道部…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道剑道部最近活动积极
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我真的觉得可惜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  他们两个今年根本没参加过比赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们真的还是剑道部的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  你不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师出去干什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在怎么说也不会被解雇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  咱们现在正干得火热
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好还会批预算下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹬鼻子上脸！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才算数？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害！段君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候学会抽胴的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在陪小都都练习的时候慢慢就记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为重心比较低  所以能比较平稳地打出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会也要告诉小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要开玩笑  勇次君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之  还有几天时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办  你考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要我考虑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了谁建立的部团啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹剑23话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好评应援中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢指导
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～完啦完啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果宫崎同学还是没赶上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们等下留一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  老师你要借钱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们回去吧  今天不用打扫了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挂在这里啊  布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说  因为他们两个要我们中止活动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整整一年？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不同意！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:13:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？为什么大家都在努力  却还要受这样的待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为学校这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太奇怪了！根本是蛮不讲理！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  这已经决定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山和岩佐  自春天开始就没有参加过正式比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习比赛也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们已经算退部的话  就和剑道部没有关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有发过退部书吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上  就算不发也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说  要甩掉他们对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说谎对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  就可以说服校方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他们的处分也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也不会抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…这样决定真的好吗？老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要决定的人不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你  纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们的部团活动的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你这个部长来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是顾问吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部团活动是你们学生的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来向学校传达你们觉得最好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天之前回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要中止活动…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是甩掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头你们转告一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你还是有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都看着小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠最近变了  好像变回原样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得像没有加入部团之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我原本就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  家里还有事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！发动啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都…做不好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎？你怎么在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到处找你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为见不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  说谎是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为输给了凯莉  所以觉得练习很痛苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！都已经那样在练习了还是不能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么练到能赢不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一起回部团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我新学会了抽胴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头也教给小都都啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎你这种有才能做什么都一帆风顺的人不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上有拼上性命练习也做不到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远也战胜不了的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我练剑道还有什么意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山他…就没做过什么像样的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也从来没打扫过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光会欺负女生做些有的没的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话…我觉得就算没他才更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩佐也从来都是见死不救的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的男生都退出了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛的时候甚至都不来为我们加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是他们自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道会这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠他们入部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山他们不来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的觉得部团活动太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这话很刺耳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实讲我不想管他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一来气氛一下就变了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道到底该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  慢慢习惯这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后变得不再看他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有一定要让小珠他们这些一年生出赛的这个理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶走他们两人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是骗人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事情了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你今天变得好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君也这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么地方变了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来  就好像急于取胜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…慢悠悠的话就会输
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时放下手里的剑怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来  自从你懂事起一直都在练剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身手和心灵都是我的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:21:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没有必要勉强继续剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我和你妈妈都不愿意看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不懂了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.82,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:27.84,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:34.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:55.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:02.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:10.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:17.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:20.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:25.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:32.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:35.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:40.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:48.05,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.82,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:27.84,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中闪耀着的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:34.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:55.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗边光着脚丫  仰望着夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.74,0:23:02.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有无法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.19,0:23:10.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮现出午时的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:17.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒劳得令人着急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:20.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:25.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}闭上眼睛倾听心中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:32.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然无法得知  它想与我相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:35.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:40.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光辉而耀眼的那小小心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:48.05,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄于手中  希望流星能为我实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.71,0:23:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是勇次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.92,0:23:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的剑道部目前正面临一连串麻烦事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.38,0:23:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.47,0:23:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但「不过是个勇次你还想干什么」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.23,0:24:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不就是个勇次还这么嚣张」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.04,0:24:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「行了吧你  勇次还是回你富良野爷爷家种地去吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.67,0:24:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人们这么喷过后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.45,0:24:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确我是勇次
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.60,0:24:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但说来这个勇次是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.82,0:24:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我思考
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.02,0:24:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我努力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.84,0:24:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为勇次要该出手时就出手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.24,0:24:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望各位能期待下回  第24话「剑与道」中登场的超级勇次
